Homepage: www.freewebs.com/wovaki --------
IMPORTANT! ****************** I recommend that you manually backup (copy & paste) the file you are going to backup BEFORE you use this program on it. This is just a precautionary step to make sure your files are safe. ******************
To Use: ------------ 1. Select the file you want to backup, and the place you want the backup to be saved. 2. Set the interval. (How often the file is backed up) 3. If the "Notfiy me when backup complete" checkbox is checked, when the program is in the tray, a message will popup everytime the file is backed up. 4. Click "Start" to start the backup process. Click "Stop" to stop it. 5. Check the log for backup information.
/////////////////////////////// /////VERSION HISTORY///// ///////////////////////////// [v1.3] - New Backup System for XML Servers. - Added Options Page. - More Backup and Program Options Added. - Fixed Error Handling.
[v1.2] - Code 100% Re-written. - Program now makes a new file every backup. (For Database only) - Right-click the log to Save or Clear it. - Minor adjustments.
[v1.1] - Backs up a file or a directory (all items in a folder).
[v1.0] - Backs up file at a set interval. - Program Minimizes to tray for more space. -----
================== ==FUTURE HOPES== ================== - None At The Moment. -----------
Please make sure to report any bugs/problems to me. I am open to all suggestions.
Signed, Wovaki
